Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}『WOLF字幕組』      (www.wolfsub.com)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.26,0:00:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光陰漫漫生如幻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕日悠悠若紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埴輪清語猶甘露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.83,0:00:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散落人間知幾年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的東西就要從世界上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是自然的法則
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,細菌先進化成魚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再經歷各類物種最後進化成人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個過程中沒用的物種都被淘汰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而現在人類消失的時候也到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們作為新物種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全新地出現在了進化的分支上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算給他們注入了黑蜜的血
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠像你們這樣在能力上覺醒的人也是鳳毛鱗角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾乎全是失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還要更多的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有玩具就要黑蜜的血
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些都是你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完不成任務只有等著被淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有鋼鐵的外殼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那瘋子面前還是不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定命運的時候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的背後有大批的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是前進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是後退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你選哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 車僧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要干蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼攔我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你何必費心思去跟一個廢物囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他充其量只是條走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你撿回條命嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經下命殲滅埴輪並奪取匿藏的御稜威
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說黑蜜在那兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:06:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易得到的第八次線索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有第八次已經不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一千多年中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經錯過了太多的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我一定要親手…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很喜歡這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論看多少次都不會厭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜歡這兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡的東西我怎麼會討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些花的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是舞子草嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世間的人雖然都這麼叫它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我用別的名字來稱呼它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就出發了 你準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 時間很緊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙仁輪會見你 還說要確認件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀先放我這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那之前你得戴上眼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的蛇已經冬眠了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪之前是不會冬眠的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想讓你吃槍子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這兒等下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我走了再拿下眼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 居座魚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼讓他去那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是向外人暴露了領袖的位置嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正需要檢驗的不是技巧和能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙仁輪會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個人都有自己要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙仁輪會檢驗人心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會在這裏保護御稜威
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御稜威
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼會在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要當心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心懷叵測的人們想要拆散我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不瞭解自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼會給周圍的人帶來恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時還會引起他們的殺心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在看到的並不是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們馬上會再見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前至少請不要忘記我們昔日的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久遠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼對待客人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是試一下這傢伙有沒有資格做我們的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請原諒久遠的無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:19:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了喚起你的記憶在蠟燭裏放了致幻劑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這朵花的名字你一定知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆之間獨有的稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磷光 Phosphorescence
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Phosphorescence:磷光;發磷光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一到晚上它就會發出微弱的青光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以黑蜜這麼叫它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著這些花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們希望這一刻能直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 這些花…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從黑蜜夫人那裏聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你希望和黑蜜夫人重溫美好的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將樂意效勞把你帶回黑蜜夫人的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能見到黑蜜?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙仁輪夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居座魚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽的 該死的赤帝軍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我刀

